# Visual Builder (`/dev/builder`)

A Figma-like visual page builder that renders SDUI components directly in the same React tree (no iframe). Built at `app/dev/builder/`.

---

## File Map

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `page.tsx` | Top-level layout: left panel + canvas + right panel. |
| `_store.ts` | Zustand store: `pageNodes`, `selectedIds`, `hoveredId`, history (undo/redo), clipboard, locked/hidden sets. Exposes `window.__builderStore` at module level (before React hydration) for Playwright. Also exports `findNode`, `findParentNode`, `REQUIRED_PARENT`, `ALLOWED_CHILDREN`. |
