## E2E Tests

Tests use `window.__builderStore` (exposed at **module level** in `_store.ts`, NOT in a `useEffect`) to read/write Zustand state directly. Available as soon as the JS bundle loads, before React hydration completes.

**`gotoBuilder` pattern:**
```ts
async function gotoBuilder(page: Page) {
  await page.goto('/dev/builder');
  await page.waitForSelector('[data-builder-page-frame]', { timeout: 30_000 });
  await page.waitForSelector('[data-testid="tab-components"]', { timeout: 15_000 });
  await page.waitForFunction(
    () => !!(window as unknown as Record<string, unknown>).__builderStore,
    { timeout: 20_000, polling: 100 }
  );
}
```

**`injectNodes` pattern** (preferred over drag-and-drop):
```ts
async function injectNodes(page: Page, nodes: unknown[]) {
  await page.evaluate((n) => {
    (window as unknown as Record<string, { getState: () => { _setPageNodes: (n: unknown[]) => void } }>)
      .__builderStore.getState()._setPageNodes(n);
  }, nodes);
  // ALL nodes must have `id` for data-builder-id to be set
  await page.waitForSelector(`[data-builder-id="${(nodes[0] as {id: string}).id}"]`, { timeout: 8_000 });
}
```

**Key helpers:**
- `gotoBuilder(page)` тАФ navigate to `/dev/builder`, wait for frame + tabs + store
- `injectNodes(page, nodes)` тАФ set page nodes directly via store (bypasses flaky drag-and-drop)
- `selectViaLayers(page)` тАФ click Layers tab тЖТ first layer-row тЖТ Design tab
- `getNodeClassName(page, nodeId)` тАФ reads `node.props.className` from store
- `getNodeStyle(page, nodeId)` тАФ reads `node.props.style` from store
- `scrollTo(page, testId)` тАФ scrolls element into view inside overflow panel container

**`beforeAll` / `beforeEach` pattern** (used in all panel spec files for performance):
```ts
let page: Page;
test.beforeAll(async ({ browser }) => { page = await browser.newPage(); await gotoBuilder(page); });
test.beforeEach(async () => {
  // clear canvas between tests instead of re-navigating
  await page.evaluate(() => {
    (window as unknown as Record<string, { getState: () => { _setPageNodes: (n: unknown[]) => void } }>)
      .__builderStore.getState()._setPageNodes([]);
  });
});
```

**Test series:**
- `BP-00`тАУ`BP-44` (in `panel-interactive.spec.ts`): Pressable-based button, all right-panel controls. Replaces old `button-panel.spec.ts` (deleted).
- `PI-01`тАУ`PI-03`: Content section for Pressable with Text children.
- `PF-01`тАУ`PF-16` (in `panel-form.spec.ts`): Input, Textarea, Checkbox, Toggle.
- `PD-01`тАУ`PD-11` (in `panel-display.spec.ts`): Heading, Badge, Avatar.
- `PM-01`тАУ`PM-10` (in `panel-media.spec.ts`): NextImage (placeholder, resize, src), NavIcon (size/color), Icon Tap.
- `T1`тАУ`T11`: Dimension, rotate, NumberInput, moveNode, drop zone, opacity.
- `U1`тАУ`U14`: Alignment, flip, auto layout, gap, clip, stroke, typography, DOM visual update.
- `V1`тАУ`V8`: Color pickers, visibility with gap, section visibility per node type, self-alignment.
- `DI-01`тАУ`DI-04`: Drop indicator direction тАФ vertical line for row/HStack, horizontal for column.
- `Fix-DropLine-1/2`: Drop line not shown over dragged node, moveNode correct index placement.

**Selection in E2E тАФ use Layers panel, not canvas click:**
Canvas click-to-select can be unreliable in Playwright/headless тАФ the capture overlay's `onPointerDown` may not fire. For tests that need a node selected, use the Layers panel instead:
```ts
await page.getByTestId('tab-layers').click();
await page.getByTestId('layer-row').first().click();
```

**Injected nodes must have `id` fields:** Without `id`, the renderer does not set `data-builder-id`, making `waitForSelector('[data-builder-id="..."]')` time out.

**Timeout:** Global Playwright timeout is `120_000`ms. All `test.setTimeout` calls use `120_000`ms. The dev server must be running on port 3001 (`npx next dev -p 3001`).

